  @{" Setting tile size  " link TileSize       }   Setting XY size of tiles
  @{" Settings window    " link SettingsWindow }   How to alter AdEd's global settings
  @{" Flags window       " link FlagsWindow    }   Setting tile flags
  @{" General usage      " link GeneralInfo    }   A guide to working with Mapper
